### ===== rec-service API Tests =====
### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8086/api/v1
@authUrl = http://localhost:8081/api/v1/auth
@travelUrl = http://localhost:8082/api/v1/travels

### ----- 1. Authentification -----

### Login en tant que TRAVELER
POST {{authUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "voyageur@test.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

> {% client.global.set("travelerToken", response.body.token); %}

### Login en tant que ADMIN
POST {{authUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@test.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

> {% client.global.set("adminToken", response.body.token); %}

### ----- 2. Recommandations -----

### Voyages populaires (public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/recommendations/popular?limit=10

### Voyages similaires (public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/recommendations/similar/{{travelId}}?limit=5

### Recommandations personnalisees (authentifie)
GET {{baseUrl}}/recommendations/personalized?limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{travelerToken}}

### ----- 3. Feedbacks -----

### Creer un feedback (TRAVELER)
POST {{baseUrl}}/feedbacks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{travelerToken}}

{
  "travelId": "{{travelId}}",
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Excellent voyage, je recommande vivement !"
}

### Feedbacks d'un voyage (public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/feedbacks/travel/{{travelId}}?page=0&size=20

### Mes feedbacks (authentifie)
GET {{baseUrl}}/feedbacks/me?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{travelerToken}}

### Modifier un feedback (TRAVELER)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/feedbacks/{{feedbackId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{travelerToken}}

{
  "rating": 4,
  "comment": "Tres bon voyage, quelques ameliorations possibles."
}

### Supprimer un feedback (TRAVELER/ADMIN)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/feedbacks/{{feedbackId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{travelerToken}}

### ----- 4. Signalements -----

### Creer un signalement (authentifie)
POST {{baseUrl}}/reports
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{travelerToken}}

{
  "reportedUserId": "{{reportedUserId}}",
  "reason": "Comportement inapproprie durant le voyage"
}

### Lister les signalements (ADMIN)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Detail d'un signalement (ADMIN)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/{{reportId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Resoudre un signalement (ADMIN)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/reports/{{reportId}}/resolve
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
